		<td bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/lotr/gfx/mom/whi_08.gif"><font class="bfont"><table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0"><tr><td colspan="2"><font class="h1font">Terrible and Evil</font></td></tr><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Rating</Font></TD><TD><table width='96' border='0' cellspacing='0' cellpadding='0'><tr><td background='/lotr/gfx/5star.gif'><img src='/lotr/gfx/trans.gif' width='1' height='25'></td></tr></table><font size=1>(4.79)</font> | <A HREF="/lotr/decks/decks.php?reviews=30937&PHPSESSID=bf5f5e4e364ddc0fc5fd5dbf04634463">Read Reviews</A></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Author</font></TD><TD><font class="bfont"> <A HREF="http://www.decktech.net/lotr/main/mpage.php?member=12792">Manuel "Goblin-Breed" Cabezalí</A></FONT> <font class="afont"> <a href='http://www.decktech.net/lotr/main/mpage.php?member=12792&sub=1'> (Subscribe to this member)</a></font></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Description</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="bfont"> Did you see Gandalf signet on Arwen? I did :-P</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Submitted</Font></TD><TD><font class="bfont"> December 1, 2003</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Cards</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="bfont"> Frodo TT<br />
The One Ring IB<br />
<br />
SITE PATH<br />
<br />
1 Exert and elf to make conditions and possessions cost +2<br />
2 Plains site. <br />
3 Add a threat to draw a card.<br />
4 Remove burdens to shoot guys. Plains site.<br />
5 Add 2 burdens or discard hand. Plains site.<br />
6 Heal each dwarf companion (well, I was looking for something that does not benefit)<br />
7 Plains site.<br />
8 Remove 2 threats to play a Nazgûl -2<br />
9 Add 3 threats. Plains site.<br />
<br />
